SOURCE: https://github.com/oasisprotocol/docs/blob/main/docs/node/mainnet/upgrade-log.md#2025-04-16_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: bash
CODE:
```
oasis-node governance gen_cast_vote \
  "${TX_FLAGS[@]}" \
  --vote.proposal.id 2 \
  --vote yes \
  --transaction.file tx_cast_vote.json \
  --transaction.nonce $NONCE \
  --transaction.fee.gas 2000 \
  --transaction.fee.amount 2000
```

